command mode.................>insert mode to change from command mode to insert mode we will use i
insert mode..................>command mode to change from insert to command we will use ESC
chmod using numeric charchter
NUMBER                        REPRESENTS               STATUS
 0                         no permission               ---    
1                           execute permission        --x
2                          write permission            -w-
3                          execute and write           -wx-
4                          read, permissions             r--
5                          read,execute                 r-x
6                          read,write                   r-w
7                          read write and execute       rwx
